Absolutely obsessed with Playboi Carti’s "Weekend"! This song is a straight-up vibe from start to finish. The production is next level, with those hauntingly melodic synths and Carti’s signature ad-libs that just hit right. It's the perfect balance of chill but hype, and it captures that carefree, weekend energy perfectly. You can’t help but get lost in the flow of it, whether you're cruising through the city or just vibing at home. Carti never disappoints, and this track is one of his most timeless yet. Total earworm – can’t stop hitting repeat! Highly recommend!
